
<div id="tutorial" class="deck-container">
    <div class="slide step1">
        <h2>This is a stream of <strong>SPARKS.</strong></h2>
        <h3>They appear on the home page and all 20 style categories.</h3>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/tutorial/step1-01.jpg') }}" alt="Stream" class="image1">
    </div>
    <div class="slide step2">
        <h2>Love a <strong>SPARK?</strong></h2>
        <h3>Save it by <span>RESPARKING</span> it to one of your own <strong>collections.</strong></h3>
        <div class="arrow"></div>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/tutorial/step2-01.jpg') }}" alt="Resparking" class="image1">
    </div>
    <div class="slide step3">
        <h2><span>RESPARKED</span> <strong>SPARKS</strong><br>go into one of your <strong>collections.</strong></h2>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/tutorial/step3-01.jpg') }}" alt="Resparked" class="image1">
