    </div>
    <div class="slide step4">
        <h2>CREATE a <strong>collection</strong> for <em>everything</em> you love.</h2>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/tutorial/step4-01.jpg') }}" alt="Colelctions" class="image1">
    </div>
    <div class="slide step5">
        <h2>See a <strong>collection</strong> you love? <strong>Follow it.</strong></h2>
        <div class="arrow1"></div>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/tutorial/step5-01.jpg') }}" alt="Follow collection" class="image1">
