        <div class="arrow2"></div>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/tutorial/step5-02.jpg') }}" alt="My Stream" class="image2">
    </div>
    <div class="slide step6">
        <h2>Add <strong>SPARKS</strong> via our Spark It! button on the ‘Add’ page.</h2>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/tutorial/step6-01.jpg') }}" alt="Add page" class="image1">
