    <div class="slide step7">
        <h2><strong>SPARK</strong> anything that inspires you & your personal style.</h2>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/tutorial/step7-01.png') }}" alt="Your style" class="image1">
    </div>
    <div class="slide step8">
        <h2>Add <strong>SPARKS</strong> via URL entry or directly uploading an image on the ‘Add’ page.</h2>
        <img src="{{ asset('images/tutorial/step8-01.png') }}" alt="Add forms" class="image1">
